{"tid":397491,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知自己做緊乜","createTime":"2017-09-12T13:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T14:27:34.000Z","uid":148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6043232abe0060b5e42998c34fec6c0d0add88cf","tid":397491,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:50:05.000Z","msg":"返咗新工個半月都仲係犯低級錯誤<br />\n月頭學過嘅野 月尾已經唔太記得點做<br />\n寫低咗睇完,做做吓又好迷惘 問完人先發現之前人地教過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做人做到咁撚垃圾 咁簡單嘅野都做唔嚟,真係唔知自己做緊乜<br />\n日日行屍走肉咁<br />\n<br />\n成日覺得喺呢個社會生存好撚辛苦,反抗政府又唔撚理你<br />\n身邊一大堆港豬,現實為咗喺返工圈子生存日日就好虛偽咁附和<br />\n但心入面其實就反共,做做吓越嚟越覺得自己好撚假<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前細個少少野都好易滿足 但人大咗就慾望多咗<br />\n會想搵多啲錢 甚至ff供得起層樓俾到好生活屋企人<br />\n可惜現實係打份牛工 一世都供唔起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人越大就越收埋自己,有咩都吞咗佢就算 都廢事講出嚟煩到人<br />\n有時屋企人問到去邊 都係呃佢地同朋友一齊,其實就係自己一個鳩行遊蕩<br />\n同事問放假去邊玩又作堆大話呃鳩佢地<br />\n次次都同自己講最後一次呻...喺香港大家都生存得咁辛苦 無謂放負搞到人<br />\n越嚟越想解脫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d22221b11066b92cdef3febcdb77eb139ed4e82","tid":397491,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:52:36.000Z","msg":"番新工 日日lunch自己食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe32ccd7ee0aab4967b8f81daa9d241b5a7c6306","tid":397491,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>番新工 日日lunch自己食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經慣咗 <br />\n唔洗應酬人唔洗煩仲好"},{"pid":"12cd1ef4691765dad0de454e6c7e2f392b7c27f0","tid":397491,"uid":97109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:56:07.000Z","msg":"要點做人先冇咁大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得大部份同事都好黑人憎"},{"pid":"700d65260f6c3b909fe757a67e8e97060afa88d6","tid":397491,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要點做人先冇咁大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得大部份同事都好黑人憎</blockquote><br />\n人際關係 係最複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33745cf2a06bedcc3fb387f1d4875def097ba934","tid":397491,"uid":97109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:02:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要點做人先冇咁大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得大部份同事都好黑人憎</blockquote><br />\n人際關係 係最複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打幾歲"},{"pid":"a2478cd4c17cac99ca6d55e871599a65c933de75","tid":397491,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要點做人先冇咁大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得大部份同事都好黑人憎</blockquote><br />\n人際關係 係最複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打幾歲</blockquote><br />\n就廿中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a812938a28b94ec2e5e5e11b717628485017385","tid":397491,"uid":97109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:23:40.000Z","msg":"試下不好對自己咁高要求    人人能力不同  <br />\n做不到叻既咪學下點做下把"},{"pid":"b9a3c99494c0728351a5a15f0c892915e604052c","tid":397491,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下不好對自己咁高要求    人人能力不同  <br />\n做不到叻既咪學下點做下把</blockquote><br />\n一直都好安守本份做個廢柴毒撚<br />\n但現實你唔進步更快俾人淘汰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}